. * ==============================================================================
. * PROGRAMAS DE REPLICACION JACKKNIFE (delete-1-cluster)
. * Un programa rclass por estadistico -- evita ambiguedad de parsing de opciones
. * dentro de jackknife (bug conocido: dispatcher con option() confunde al parser
. * en llamadas subsecuentes dentro del mismo do-file).
. * ==============================================================================
. capture program drop jk_gini_theil

. program define jk_gini_theil, rclass
  1.     syntax [if]
  2.     marksample touse
  3.     quietly ineqdeco ingpc [aw=fexp] if `touse'
  4.     return scalar gini = r(gini)
  5.     return scalar ge0  = r(ge0)
  6. end

. 
. capture program drop jk_pobreza

. program define jk_pobreza, rclass
  1.     syntax [if]
  2.     marksample touse
  3.     quietly summarize pobre_ingresos [aw=fexp] if `touse'
  4.     return scalar p_ingresos = r(mean)
  5.     quietly summarize pobre_extremo [aw=fexp] if `touse'
  6.     return scalar p_extremo  = r(mean)
  7. end

. 
. capture program drop jk_ipm

. program define jk_ipm, rclass
  1.     syntax [if]
  2.     marksample touse
  3.     quietly summarize ipm_pobre [aw=fexp] if `touse'
  4.     return scalar ipm = r(mean)
  5. end

. 
. capture program drop jk_idh

. program define jk_idh, rclass
  1.     syntax [if]
  2.     marksample touse
  3.     quietly summarize idh_proxy_td [aw=fexp] if `touse'
  4.     return scalar idh = r(mean)
  5. end

